description: Cygnus aims to Decentralize the internet disrupting the web browser industry while incentivizing the use of blockchain technology. Cygnus is the first freeware blockchain-based decentralized web browser app, the purpuse is to provide a decentralized way of web browsing built and supported by the blockchain and its own cryptocurrency (CYG) which can be used for in-app purchases and app-related payment solutions such as rewards, traded , used as a store of value and in the future as a payment method for the purchase of goods and services, we also want to build a strong community to find market solutions toghether and a charity program to help people all over around the world to make them live in financial freedom.
name: Cygnus
